1. Vehicle Details (Gadi Ki Information):

Critical Details: Vehicle license ke basis par ye details important hain:

Make: (Brand, e.g., Toyota, Honda).

Model: (e.g., Corolla, Civic).

Year: Manufacturing year.

Engine Capacity: Engine size.

Vehicle Age: Gadi ki age premium ko affect nahi karti, kyunki flat premium charge hota hai.


2. Coverage Types (Policy Ke Options):

Comprehensive Cover: Gadi ke full protection ke liye (theft, accident, damage).

Third-Party Cover: Sirf third-party liabilities ke liye (jaise kisi aur ki property ka nuksaan).

Add-Ons: Special coverage options:

Personal Accident Cover: Driver aur passengers ke liye injury/death cover.

Windscreen Cover: Broken windscreen ke liye replacement.
Towing and Emergency Assistance: Breakdown par towing help.

Replacement Vehicle Cover: Gadi repair ke time temporary replacement.

Loss of Use Cover: Gadi ke repair ke time daily allowance.


3. Driver Details (Driver Ki Information):

Premium Calculation: Driver ki age, experience, ya accident history ka koi farq nahi padta. Flat premium lagta 
hai.

High-Risk Profiles: Young drivers ya traffic violations ka impact premium par nahi hota.


4. Premium Factors (Premium Kaise Calculate Hoga):

Car Value-Based Premium: Gadi ki value ke basis par premium decide hota hai.

Location/Usage Type: Driving location ya usage type (personal vs. commercial) ka koi effect nahi.


5. Claims Processing (Claim File Karne Ke Rules):

Documents Required:

Police Report: Accident/incident ka official report.

Claim Form: Insurer ka claim form fill karna hoga.

Vehicle Registration: Gadi ka registration certificate.

Driver's License: Driver ka valid license.

Proof of Ownership: Gadi ka ownership proof (certificate ya bill of sale).

Estimate of Repairs: Authorized repairer se repair ka estimate.

Photographs: Damage aur evidence ki photos.

Limits & Deductibles:

Deductible: Har claim par fixed amount (e.g., ₦50,000).

Excess: Claim amount ka percentage (e.g., 10%).

Depreciation: Repair cost par 10%-20% depreciation deduct hoga.

Maximum Claim Limit: Ek claim par maximum payout (e.g., ₦5 million).

Aggregate Claim Limit: Policy year me total maximum payout (e.g., ₦10 million).
















<!-- /////////////////////////////// -->
1. Vehicle Details (Gadi Ki Information Kya Zaroori Hai):

Critical Details: Vehicle ki basic information important hai, jo license se milti hai:

Make: Gadi ka brand (e.g., Toyota, Honda).

Model: Specific variant (e.g., Corolla, Civic).

Year: Gadi kab bani thi (manufacturing year).

Engine Capacity: Engine ki size (e.g., 1.6L, 2.0L).

Vehicle Age Ka Impact:

Gadi ki umar premium ko affect nahi karti, kyunki flat premium lagta hai (sab ke liye ek hi rate).


2. Coverage Types (Kaun-Kaun Se Options Dene Hain):

Comprehensive Cover:

Full protection ke liye, including:

Accident damage (aapki gadi ke liye).

Theft (gadi chori hone par).

Natural disasters ya fire damage.

Third-Party Cover:

Ye mandatory hai, aur sirf third-party liabilities cover karta hai:

Kisi aur ki property ka nuksaan.

Kisi aur ko injury hone par expenses.

Special Add-Ons (Optional):


Personal Accident Cover: Driver aur passengers ke injury/death ka cover.

Windscreen Cover: Broken ya damaged windscreen ka replacement.

Towing and Emergency Assistance: Gadi breakdown hone par towing help.

Replacement Vehicle Cover: Repair ke dino ke liye temporary gadi.

Loss of Use Cover: Repair ke waqt daily allowance.


3. Driver Details (Driver Ki Information Ka Kya Role Hai):

Premium Calculation:

Driver ki age, experience, ya accident history ka premium par koi asar nahi.

Flat premium lagta hai sab ke liye.

High-Risk Profiles:

Young drivers ya traffic violations ke cases me bhi premium constant hai, koi change nahi hota.


4. Premium Factors (Premium Kaise Decide Hoga):

Value-Based Premium:

Premium gadi ki market value ke basis par decide hota hai.

Location/Usage Type:

Driving location ya personal/commercial usage ka koi impact nahi.


5. Claims Processing (Claim Kaise File Karna Hai):

Documents Jo Zaroori Hain:

Police Report: Nigerian Police ka official report jo incident ko explain kare.

Claim Form: Insurance company ka filled claim form.

Vehicle Registration: Gadi ka registration certificate ka copy.

Driver's License: Valid driver’s license ka copy.

Proof of Ownership: Gadi ke ownership ka proof (certificate ya bill of sale).

Estimate of Repairs: Authorized repairer ka detailed repair estimate.

Photographs: Gadi ke damage aur incident ki photos.

Limits & Deductibles (Jo Policyholder Ko Pay Karna Padega):



Deductible: Har claim ke liye fixed amount (e.g., ₦50,000).

Excess: Claim amount ka ek percentage (e.g., 10%).


Depreciation: Gadi ke parts ke liye 10%-20% depreciation charge hoga.

Maximum Claim Limit: Ek claim ke liye maximum payout (e.g., ₦5 millio
n).

Aggregate Claim Limit: Puri policy year me sabhi claims ke liye maximum payout (e.g., ₦10 million).

Simplified Summary for Client:

Flat Premiums: Driver ki age, experience, ya gadi ki umar ka koi effect nahi.

Comprehensive & Third-Party Options: Dono options honge, taaki client ki zarurat ke hisab se choose kar sake.

Add-Ons: Useful extra covers jaise accident cover, towing assistance, aur replacement vehicle ka option milega.

Value-Based Premium: Premium gadi ki value ke basis par hoga, transparent aur simple calculation ke saath.

Claims: Process clear hai—documents aur limits predefined hain, taaki koi confusion na ho.